  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lost In Static is a first-person psychological horror experience. Discover a surreal and unsettling mall where reality blurs and sanity is frail. You were meant to enjoy a simple day out with your daughter, but after you were rendered unconscious you awake and arrive in the backrooms. <strong>Your task? Find your daughter and get the hell out.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features: </strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TV Remote</strong>: Allows you to teleport around the map.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Notes</strong>: Clues, hints how to survive, and a look into the past. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Liminal Space:</strong> Navigate the liminal space hallways.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survive:</strong> Evade the anomalous entities.  <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use the TVs to teleport: </strong>There are malfunctioning TVs around the map. Manipulate their wavelengths to teleport.  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180420/extras/34d3cf0ab5341b60919929f2009b8986.poster.avif?t=1772675867\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180420/extras/34d3cf0ab5341b60919929f2009b8986.webm?t=1772675867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180420/extras/34d3cf0ab5341b60919929f2009b8986.mp4?t=1772675867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Follow the notes: </strong>Read the notes to uncover what has happened, or to find hints how to survive the monsters. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180420/extras/981181d03c6448dc47beb1973eb84a03.poster.avif?t=1772675867\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180420/extras/981181d03c6448dc47beb1973eb84a03.webm?t=1772675867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180420/extras/981181d03c6448dc47beb1973eb84a03.mp4?t=1772675867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Traverse the liminal space: </strong>Weave your way through the liminal spaces and try not to get caught.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180420/extras/290ed50f379fe34f6993d1155fbba8ec.poster.avif?t=1772675867\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180420/extras/290ed50f379fe34f6993d1155fbba8ec.webm?t=1772675867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180420/extras/290ed50f379fe34f6993d1155fbba8ec.mp4?t=1772675867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180420/extras/5a1bcf6f9f35dba48693441bd836c48e.poster.avif?t=1772675867\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180420/extras/5a1bcf6f9f35dba48693441bd836c48e.webm?t=1772675867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180420/extras/5a1bcf6f9f35dba48693441bd836c48e.mp4?t=1772675867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Run from the anomalous entities you find: </strong>You aren't the only thing with a mission. Watch out for different creatures.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180420/extras/98c86095ce2e34780ec8c1cb4b066f0e.poster.avif?t=1772675867\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180420/extras/98c86095ce2e34780ec8c1cb4b066f0e.webm?t=1772675867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180420/extras/98c86095ce2e34780ec8c1cb4b066f0e.mp4?t=1772675867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180420/extras/5d04d332ea89a3c1b2fe2a33a5044b13.poster.avif?t=1772675867\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180420/extras/5d04d332ea89a3c1b2fe2a33a5044b13.webm?t=1772675867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180420/extras/5d04d332ea89a3c1b2fe2a33a5044b13.mp4?t=1772675867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
